$$1 - P(\text{at least one match}) = \sum_{k=0}^{n} \frac{(-1)^k}{k!} \to e^{-1}$$

So: $P(\text{at least one match}) \to 1 - e^{-1} = 1 - 0.36788 = 0.63212$

Summary: The final answer is $0.632$
